	REGEXXER_HAVE_GTKMM_22 if available.

	* src/controller.cc:
	* src/mainwindow.cc:
	* src/statusline.cc: If building for gtkmm >= 2.1.0, make use of
	atkmm to set names and descriptions of several GUI elements.

